sentences: Jill Carnes is an Elephant 6-related musician and artist.
She performs as Thimble Circus with Eric Harris, and self-released one album under that name, Lullaby for Worriers, in 2003.
The album features appearances by Elephant 6 artists and associates Peter Erchick, Chris Jolly, Heather McIntosh, Scott Spillane, and Jeff Mangum.
